These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-1::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, cricket, skiing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Pet     | ferret | goat    | pony   |
| Sport   | golf  | skiing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, mirinda
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, spy, romance
1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | water   | mirinda  | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | superhero | romance    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, malaysian, german
3 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, ferret
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the british is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
4. the german is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german | british |
| Pet           | turtle    | ferret     | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-4::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, cabbage, zucchini
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
2. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
3. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food    | zucchini | blueberry     | cabbage   |
| Sport   | snowboarding   | sailing | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, pakistani, russian
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, helicopter, airplane
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the colombian##1
3. the russian is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | colombian | russian   |
| Transport     | helicopter | airplane    | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, rock, blues
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | writing | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | rock   | blues        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, pilot, journalist
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
2. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
3. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |     2      |         3          |
| Job     | writer | journalist    | pilot |
| Sport   | rugby      | sailing | baseball             |

