.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, writer, photographer
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the musician is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the musician is somewhere to the left of the writer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | camping | puzzles  | chess    |
| Job     | photographer   | musician | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage    | juice       | almond-milk   | iced-tea |
| Transport   | motorbike | bus | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, manager, entrepreneur
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, blues, disco
1. the entrepreneur is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
3. the fan of pop is between the fan of disco and the fan of blues##2
4. the manager is on the left of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job           | nurse | manager | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | pop      | disco    |

