There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, german, indonesian
1. the german is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | water   | coffee     | juice      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | german | canadian |

