.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-12::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, spinach, peas
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, bike
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |    3    |
| Food        | kale | spinach | peas |
| Transport   | helicopter  | jet-ski         | bike   |

