.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, d&b, blues
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | blues          | d&b     | punk  |
| Sport         | skiing | ice-hockey | rugby |

