The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, romance
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
2. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | fanta | iced-tea  | coffee         |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | spy | romance |

