2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
3. the lawyer is on the left of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Job     | lawyer | analyst   | scientist   |
| Sport   | water-polo | skiing | tennis |

