3. the chinese is on the right of the italian##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality   | australian | italian       | chinese |
| Sport         | climbing | cycling | weightlifting |

