3 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, chinchilla
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | chinchilla  | cat    | ferret    |

