.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, funk, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, trike
1. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | hip-hop | soul  |
| Transport     | motorbike | trike   | airplane |

 